{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"sum","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/sum","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div style=\"background:#f5f5f5; margin: 5px 0;\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <b><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XSLT/Transforming_XML_with_XSLT/The_Netscape_XSLT_XPath_Reference\">XSLT/XPath Reference</a></b>: <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XSLT/Element\">XSLT elements</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT\">EXSLT functions</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions\">XPath functions</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Axes\">XPath axes</a>\n</div>\n<p>The <code>sum</code> function returns a number that is the sum of the numeric values of each node in a given node-set.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">sum(node-set)\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"arguments","title":"Arguments","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"node-set\"><code>node-set</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The node-set to be evaluated. Each node in this node-set is evaluated as if it were passed to the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/number\">number()</a> function, and a sum of the resulting numbers is returned.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"returns","title":"Returns","isH3":true,"content":"<p>A number.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"Notes","isH3":true,"content":"<p>None.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"defined","title":"Defined","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/1999/REC-xpath-19991116/#function-sum\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">XPath 1.0 4.3</a></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gecko_support","title":"Gecko support","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Supported.</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"The sum function returns a number that is the sum of the numeric values of each n